<p>Fortune! Prosperity! This is the 33rd year of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>sarivarman. <supplied reason="lost">For</supplied> Mahāde<supplied reason="lost">va</supplied> of Ti<supplied reason="lost">ru</supplied>vālantuṟai of Ciṟupaḻuvūr, <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> of Kuṉṟakkū<supplied reason="lost">ṟṟam</supplied>, the Lord <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>uṭaiyāṉ</foreign></supplied> of Ciṟṟa<gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> of <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>nāṭu, Vicciyaṉ <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, gave <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vait</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>ta</foreign></supplied></supplied> to burn <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>eriya</foreign></supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>, as long as the sun and the moon endure <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ca</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>ntrā</foreign></supplied><foreign>ditya</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>val</foreign></supplied></supplied>, a perpetual lamp <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>no</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>n</foreign></supplied><foreign>tāviḷakku</foreign></supplied>; he gave <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vaitta</foreign></supplied> undying and non-ageing great goats <supplied reason="explanation"><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>cā</foreign></supplied><foreign>vāmūvāpperā</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>ṭu</foreign></supplied></supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> goats <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>āṭu</foreign></supplied> were given <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>vaitta</foreign></supplied> to burn <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>eriya</foreign></supplied> a perpetual lamp <supplied reason="explanation"><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>nontāvi</foreign></supplied><foreign>ḷakku</foreign></supplied>; <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> for this lamp <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ivviḷakkiṉu</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>kku</foreign></supplied></supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> <foreign>kaḻañcu</foreign>s <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>kaḻañyu </foreign>&gt; <foreign>kaḻañcu</foreign></supplied> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/> under the protection <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>ra</foreign><supplied reason="lost"><foreign>kṣ</foreign></supplied><foreign>ai</foreign></supplied> of the <supplied reason="lost">Panmāhe</supplied>śvarar.<note>The<foreign>panmāhe</foreign> is not engraved.</note></p></div>

